On "cheating"

It's your puzzle;

you paid for it;

solve it any way that gives you pleasure;

feel free to change your "rules" as you get more experience.

If you're in a competition with others, there needs to be rules established that create a level playing field.

Otherwise, you're on your own.

What's the problem?

